fulltitle: Church Committee: Covert Action in Chile, 1963-73 (BC.1)
title: Church Committee: Covert Action in Chile, 1963-73 (BC.1)
description:
'Our Hidden History' Audiobooks: https://sellfy.com/OurHiddenHistory This is The Church Committee's "Covert Action in Chile 1963-73" (Part One: "Overview and Background"). The official name of the Church Committee was "Senate Select Committee To Study Governmental Operations With Respect to Intelligence Activities". A copy of the report may also be found on the U.S. Senate Select Committee on Intelligence web site: http://www.intelligence.senate.gov/pdfs94th/94chile.pdf

I. Overview and Background
    i. List of Authors 00:25
   ii. Preface 01:16
    A. Overview: Covert Action in Chile 02:25
    B. Issues
    C. Historical Background in Recent United States-Chilean Relations

This audio recreation was narrated by John Hawkes (https://www.fiverr.com/johnhawkes) and produced by D. Giglio for 'Our Hidden History'

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
